author: bayard
msg: Merger of jakarta-taglibs' to be commited org.apache.taglibs.string.util
package into the Commons.Util package.
Mainly meant the addition of:
Soundex             US English Soundex. Plan to add other languages.
NumberUtils
ClassUtils
CollectionsUtils
XmlUtils
Of which, CollectionsUtils has the same name as a class in the
Commons.Collections sub-project, but no common functionality.
CollectionsUtils does have a contained class which is virtually identical
to a similar class in Commons.Collections. This should be easy to remove in
the future. Merging the methods in CollectionsUtils in with the
Commons.Collections implementation also seems pretty easy.
Also the addition of a large number of methods to StringUtils, and a few
package scoped classes in the same source file. These may wish to be pulled out.Some of the methods are duplicates of API, but function differently.
Decisions to be made at a later date as to which should be chosen etc.
